      • getTrimmedList

        private org.apache.commons.math3.stat.descriptive.DescriptiveStatistics getTrimmedList(org.apache.commons.math3.stat.descriptive.DescriptiveStatistics inputRange)
        Gets a "trimmed" list of values from a DescriptiveStatistics object. Pulls any values out of the list that are more than 1 standard deviation from the mean.
        Parameters:
        inputRange - The original list of values to be "trimmed"
        Returns:
        A new list of values, containing only those values that were within 1 standard deviation of the original mean
